# Hify 项目 Git 属性配置
# ======================
# 统一行尾符、定义 diff 行为、标记二进制文件。

# ── 行尾符规范 ────────────────────────────────────
# 所有文本文件自动使用 LF（Unix 风格）
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 批处理脚本保留 CRLF
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

# ── 文本文件类型 ──────────────────────────────────
# Java / Spring Boot
*.java text diff=java
*.properties text
*.yml text diff=yaml
*.yaml text diff=yaml
*.xml text diff=xml
*.sql text
*.md text diff=markdown
*.json text

# Vue / 前端
*.js text
*.ts text
*.vue text
*.css text
*.scss text
*.html text diff=html
*.json text

# 构建脚本
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
pom.xml text diff=xml

# ── 二进制文件（禁止 diff）─────────────────────────
# 图片
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg text

# 字体
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary

# 文档
*.pdf binary
*.doc binary
*.docx binary
*.xls binary
*.xlsx binary
*.ppt binary
*.pptx binary

# 压缩包
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.7z binary
*.rar binary

# Java 构建产物
*.jar binary
*.war binary
*.ear binary
*.class binary

# 其他
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
